reviewText: This DVD is "ok." The message is great, but the animation is lacking. Seems like it was probably made years ago before technology had gotten as advanced as it is now.
I got it and it stops playing even though it has no visible scratches. I think my DVD came defective. Other than that I love Bedbug Bible Gang
